{"tid":561724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】【不再做奴隸】澳女厭棄朝九晚五回歸自然 不穿衣不化妝自耕自吃","createTime":"2018-02-15T08:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T09:48:58.000Z","uid":41423,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b04eec122cddb445705c14d8f42d4743b89314","tid":561724,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:49:28.000Z","msg":"一般人大半生都在營營役役，澳洲一名37歲YouTuber厭棄了再做打工奴隸，決定回歸山林解放自我，她不穿衣服不化妝、耕種蔬果自給自足，享受著自然又恬靜的生活。<br />\n<br />\n來自澳洲昆士蘭的弗爾里(Freelee)跟伴侶遁入南美洲一處深山，她最近拍片上載到YouTube，向外界展示她的新生活。他倆住在一間木屋中，早上會踏單車，在戶外沖澡－－蓮蓬頭就附在他們種的樹木上。<br />\n早餐是新鮮採摘他們種植的水果，例如有大樹菠蘿，午餐則是自家種的木瓜和香蕉，「零食」是隨手採摘的「甜葉」，喝的水來自附近小溪。除了耕種，日間有甚麼好做？她會用棕櫚葉編織蓆子。<br />\n弗爾里說︰「我把自己由朝九晚五的奴隸生活中解放出來，搬到林中。日間我多數時間都裸著身，擺脫衣服的束縛，我主要吃的是由大地中採摘的有機蔬果。」她用雨水洗澡，喝溪水，「我脫離不健康的關係，找到安寧」。<br />\n生活回歸自然，外在許多物質牽絆也可以放棄，弗爾里說在過去近一年她不再化妝、不用洗頭水，「我不再為身體脫毛、染頭髮、不化妝超過6個月&hellip;&hellip;我覺得生活前所未有的自由。請別害怕與眾不同，反而要害怕變得跟所有人一樣。你自己就是一個『限量版』。」<br />\n弗爾里說她是在某個慣常早起上班的日子突然醒悟，「我厭倦了朝九晚五的框框︰用鬧鐘叫醒自己，搭一小時車上班，穿著拘謹的套裝、往臉上塗彩，用高跟鞋束縛雙腳，再掛上虛假的笑容」。她希望過著有意義的日子，於是決心回歸自然。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180215/57832320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180215%2F57832320&d=IBHhdrFBJbQzXrIVFJJjuZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=269f0232\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180215%2F57832320&h=838b4672\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180215/57832320</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180214/large/1518595162_fbbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180214%2Flarge%2F1518595162_fbbe.jpg&h=7dad42fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180214/large/1518595145_6e72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180214%2Flarge%2F1518595145_6e72.jpg&h=1cf4b8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180214/large/1518595146_6d59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180214%2Flarge%2F1518595146_6d59.jpg&h=3d608b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180214/large/1518595148_82ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180214%2Flarge%2F1518595148_82ee.jpg&h=5121fdd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8b7949e40fdfa1167ea1ab02d388fc3410b266c","tid":561724,"uid":26752,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"回歸大自然但係用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce5da7653fab819c93383c00b0d670ea6b3669e","tid":561724,"uid":170365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8b7949e40fdfa1167ea1ab02d388fc3410b266c","tid":561724,"uid":26752,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"回歸大自然但係用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"唔駛搵食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ae93d16c54ebecb84de608432167c230229a3f","tid":561724,"uid":41423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d8b7949e40fdfa1167ea1ab02d388fc3410b266c","tid":561724,"uid":26752,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"回歸大自然但係用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"偽文青<br />\n放上youtube呃like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1459844c8b234ae058b0dd47991bccf833b572ea","tid":561724,"uid":32577